      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELLIE UNLEASHED (1) has a strong winning strike-rate over this track and trip with two wins and a placing from six tries. Was out of the placings last time (20.21) at this track in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 5.5 lengths. Appeals as a leading chance in this. VELOCITY COMMIT (2) comes off an average effort last start when seventh at Q Straight over 350m behind Unacceptable Col (19.38) in a Grade 5. Was in the money prior to that. Can figure in the finish. FOXY FAWN (7) hasn't been far away, finishing in the money twice in a row including last time in a Grade 5 at Q Straight over 300m. This looks easier and expected to improve sharply. LOST YOUR MARKER (8) was strongly fancied on the back of a win two starts back but finished second last time (18.96) at Q Straight.",
